definitions.definition: A young dog , wolf , fox , seal , bat or shark , or the young of certain other animals.
examples: The dog has had that bed since he was just a pup .
The new teacher is a mere pup .

definitions.definition: Any cute dog, regardless of age.
examples: My pup likes to run as fast as he can, yet cannot always stop in time!

definitions.definition: A short semi-trailer used jointly with a dolly and another semi-trailer to create a twin trailer .
A new plant growing from a shoot that can be used for propagation.
An early edition of a periodical publication , intended for distribution to distant locations.
Someone who participates in pup play ( the sexual practice of role-playing as a young dog ) .
A small tributary or feeder stream in the US state of Alaska .
